            {
              "content": "=You are analyzing an email related to account security.\n\nClassify the email into exactly one of these categories:\n- \"security_alert\" = suspicious login, password reset, fraud warning, unusual activity, verification of a security event\n- \"otp\" = one-time passcode, verification code, login code, two-factor authentication code\n- \"account_update\" = account changes, profile updates, password changed confirmation, email changed confirmation, settings updated\n- \"none\" = none of the above\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in this format:\n\n{\n  \"category\": \"security_alert | otp | account_update | none\",\n  \"type\": \"short description\",\n  \"riskLevel\": \"low | medium | high\"\n}\n\nRules:\n- Use \"otp\" only if the email clearly contains a verification code or one-time password\n- Use \"security_alert\" for suspicious activity, fraud, login warnings, or urgent security notices\n- Use \"account_update\" for normal account change confirmations or update notices\n- Use \"none\" if the email is unrelated to security\n\nEmail Subject:\n{{ $('Gmail Body Cleaner').item.json.subject }}\n\nSender:\n{{ $('Gmail Body Cleaner').item.json.fromEmail }}\n\nEmail Body:\n{{ $('Gmail Body Cleaner').item.json.cleanBody }}"
